One More Interesting Identity

There’s a deeper one many people find beautiful:

The identity relating exponential growth and rotation:

e^{i\pi} + 1 = 0

This equation links:
	•	exponential growth
	•	imaginary numbers
	•	π (geometry)
	•	1 (multiplicative identity)
	•	0 (additive identity)

All in one place.

